        <Parent_String>West Persian textile styles after the Mongols [300244068], Persian textile styles after the Mongols [300244064], Iranian Islamic styles after the Mongols [300244126], Iranian Islamic styles and periods after the Mongols [300244063], Islamic World dynastic styles and periods [300021520], Islamic World, The [300021516], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
